{"tid":1616860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4/10 全民宣傳裝修原因＋18區和你唱","createTime":"2019-10-03T14:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T15:14:48.000Z","uid":182802,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"28404a754483c17bae5cde8cfd432b14906939b8","tid":1616860,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"好多中老年淺黃唔明點解我地要裝修<br />\n聽日唱歌會有大量淺黃和理非出現，係最理想文宣時間去幫佢地跟上前線思維<br />\n而且成個場都係手足，夠安全<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每人多有多印少有少印，至少善用學校公司資源起碼印10-20 張傳單派，主打中老年手足</span></span><br />\n每人派少少好快就派完<br />\n當每區至少<span style=\"color: red;\">10</span>個手足派，每人印<span style=\"color: red;\">20</span> 張, 聽日唱完歌都已經教育左<span style=\"color: red;\">3600 </span>個和理非 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁當然airdrop 要同時進行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n＊每人都做多少少效果好可觀，希望以後大家都可以善用和理非活動做宣傳，將圍爐時間變做有實際宣傳力量嘅大型文宣日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8sWopPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8sWopPE.jpg&h=a4a6270a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BsxCugk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBsxCugk.jpg&h=3a580176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kcmPkn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkcmPkn6.jpg&h=1525f905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUv8AZj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUv8AZj.jpg&h=769119b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4462a5877d39eb91b434b365ad74fb57e3a621f2","tid":1616860,"uid":182802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n網上日程表<br />\n(兩個都可以放埋係Google Calendar 用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n1)